---
title: Father's Day Grilled Steak and Balsamic Onions with Summer Salad and Cheesy Garlic Bread
description: Tonight we're putting an Italian-inspired steak on the grill for dad. Enjoy this meal al-fresco with summer salad, melty cheesy garlic bread, and balsamic onions to finish it all off!
